node.text:
Enjoy this 30 minute all-levels flow brought to you by @thebalancedbachelorette 🧘‍♀️ 

TBB provides everything you’ll need for a relaxing yoga class right to your hotel or Airbnb. All classes can be tailored to meet the needs and requests of your group. Hangover, or lack thereof 😉 

Heading to Scottsdale for your BACH? You can book a class with them on the BACH app!

node.text:

We are in LOVE with this Bachelorette (ABC) themed BACH party from @gabby__montes! 

A sneak peak into their weekend filmed in Paso Robles, CA: 

🌹First night was dinner & drinks

🍷Second was a long fun day of wine tasting at 3 vineyards and dinner out 

📲 Be sure to download the BACH app to plan your perfect party! 

#bacheloretteparty #bachelorettethemes #thebachelorette #bacheloretteabc #maidofhonor #weddingplanning
